### 변수 설정
@id = 1
@username = user123

### 회원가입 (POST는 permitAll)
POST {{host}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "new-user",
  "password": "secret123",
  "name": "New User",
  "email": "new.user@example.com",
  "userType": "USER",
  "trialCount": 0
}

### 사용자 전체 조회
GET {{host}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 사용자 단건 조회
GET {{host}}/api/users/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### username으로 사용자 조회
GET {{host}}/api/users/detail?username={{username}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 사용자 수정
PUT {{host}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "username": "user123",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "email": "john.updated@example.com",
  "userType": "USER",
  "trialCount": 1
}

### 사용자 삭제
DELETE {{host}}/api/users/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
